    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Man-made slands created by landfill, or diking and filling in a body of water.  Human-made islands; examples are those created by landfill or by diking and filling in a wetland, bay, or lagoon.</Note_Text>
